item.title: Confidence
item.author: lijiufeng97@gmail.com (Jiufeng Li)
item.description: 1. I appreciate the confidence I’ve built and radiate—it’s something I’ve accumulated step by step on my own, something I’ve given myself rather than received from others. So, I’m grateful to myself.
